---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="overflow-x-hidden pt-24">

    <section class="px-6 pt-8 pb-24 mx-auto max-w-7xl lg:px-8 mb-16">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <span class="font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-brand text-sm mb-4 block">About me</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl tracking-[-0.07em] text-balance sm:text-7xl">I am Valentina Díaz B. </h1>

      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">

        <div class="md:col-span-5">
          <p class="text-l leading-relaxed">I didn't start my career in a design studio, but in front of
            a compiler. <strong>As a Computer Engineer turned Product Designer,</strong> I approach every project with a
            dual lens: an obsession with high-end visual aesthetics and a deep understanding of technical feasibility.
            This hybrid background allows me to bridge the gap between complex backend logic and seamless, human-centric
            interfaces.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-8">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-brand bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
              📱 Lead Product Designer
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-brand bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
              👩🏻‍💻 Informatics Engineer
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-brand bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
              📸 Analog Experience Lover
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-brand bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
              🧩 Design Systems and Design Ops Specialist
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-7 flex items-center justify-center w-full h-full">
          <img src="/me.png" alt="About me folder" class="w-[85%] md:w-full max-w-lg h-auto object-contain shrink-0">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-brand">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center w-full">
        <h2 class="text-5xl tracking-[-0.07em] text-balance sm:text-6xl mb-12">Technical Stack & Expertise</h2>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto pb-4 px-6 lg:px-8">
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">⭐️ Figma</span>

          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">⭐️ Stakeholder Management</span>

            <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">⭐️ Design
            Systems</span>

          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">⭐️ Mentoring</span>

          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">⭐️ Design
            Ops</span>

          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">AI
            Prompting</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">React</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">Tailwind
            CSS</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">Astro</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">Lottie
            / Motion</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">Git</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">Advanced
            Prototyping</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm cursor-default whitespace-nowrap">OOUX</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-6 py-24 mx-auto max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-32">

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center w-full gap-8">
          <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-3xl">
            <h2
					  class="mt-2 text-left text-5xl tracking-[-0.07em] text-balance sm:text-6xl">The Technical Rigor behind the Pixel</h2>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">My engineering background defines how I approach design. I don't just aim for visual beauty; I ensure
              products are logically consistent and technically scalable. I have audited extensive Figma libraries and
              migrated multi-brand design systems (Web, iOS, Android) at EPAM for Fortune 500 clients, guaranteeing 100%
              alignment between design and development. I am a firm believer in democratizing design through solid Design
              Ops and clear governance, establishing efficient workflows that boost team velocity without sacrificing
              visual quality.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full sm:flex-1 flex justify-center">
            <img src="/cursor.jpg" alt="Cursor icon" class="w-20 sm:w-40 shrink-0 object-contain" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center w-full gap-8">
          <div class="w-full sm:flex-1 flex justify-center order-last sm:order-first">
            <img src="/eye.png" alt="Eye icon" class="w-50 sm:w-100 shrink-0 object-contain" />
          </div>
          <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-3xl">
            <h2
					  class="mt-2 text-right text-5xl tracking-[-0.07em] text-balance sm:text-6xl">A Curated Visual Eye</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-right leading-relaxed">Beyond systems, I possess a passion for premium aesthetics and visual storytelling. This facet is nurtured
              by my exploration of analog photography and creative direction, where organizational rigor meets visual
              curation. I bring this critical eye to every interface, utilizing advanced prototyping and
              micro-interactions (Lottie, motion standards) to elevate the final user experience. I understand a brand not
              as a logo, but as a holistic experience that must be polished and consistent at every digital touchpoint.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>